<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v14" title="Q30_v14" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      La fórmula de Euler establece que para cierto tipo de poliedros se cumple la relación 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>C</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mi>V</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mi>A</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
      </m:math>,
      donde C es la cantidad de caras, A es la cantidad de aristas y V es la cantidad de vértices del poliedro.
    </p>
    <p>
      En una ficha técnica de un poliedro se muestran los siguientes datos:
      Caras (C): ___; Vértices (V): 6; Aristas (A): 15.
      En un recuadro de la ficha se recuerda la fórmula de Euler indicada en el párrafo anterior.
      ¿Qué número debe escribirse en el espacio en blanco de "Caras (C)" para que la ficha sea coherente con la fórmula?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">23<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si C = 23, entonces C + V = 23 + 6 = 29, mientras que A + 2 = 15 + 2 = 17. Como 29 ≠ 17, esta opción no hace coherente la ficha con la fórmula.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">11<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si C = 11, entonces C + V = 11 + 6 = 17 y A + 2 = 15 + 2 = 17. Como ambos lados son iguales, la ficha sí es coherente con la fórmula de Euler.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">9<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si C = 9, entonces C + V = 9 + 6 = 15, mientras que A + 2 = 15 + 2 = 17. Como 15 ≠ 17, esta opción no satisface la fórmula.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">7<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si C = 7, entonces C + V = 7 + 6 = 13, mientras que A + 2 = 15 + 2 = 17. Como 13 ≠ 17, esta opción no satisface la fórmula.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso con la fórmula de Euler</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la fórmula y reemplazar los datos conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Como el problema indica que <strong>V = 6</strong> y <strong>A = 15</strong>, se reemplaza:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Resolver la suma del lado derecho</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>17</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces la ecuación queda:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>17</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Despejar C</strong></p>
            <p>Para encontrar la cantidad de caras, restamos 6 en ambos lados:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>17</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular el resultado</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>17</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>11</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Por lo tanto:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>11</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El número que debe escribirse en el espacio en blanco de Caras (C) es <strong>11</strong>, que corresponde a la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>